column1: 19801575_21,s0,T1,T5,,Hyou1, heterozygosity aggravates ER stress in ,Sil1,"-/- Purkinje cells. BiP upregulation in lobule II (A-D) or lobule X (E-H) of cerebella from 6-week-old Sil1-/- (A, B, E, F) and Sil1-/-; Hyou1+/- mice (C, D, G, H).
